      "para_id": "Q001111.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) For Ninĝirsu , Enlil’s warrior ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001111.3",
      "line_range": "3",
      "translation": "(i 3) En-metena , ruler of Lagaš , chosen by Nanše in the heart , chief governor of Ninĝirsu , given wisdom by Enki , child of En-ana-tum , ruler of Lagaš , for Ninĝirsu , his master who loves him , constructed the garden of the personal quarters . ... its entrance ...."
    }
  ],
